OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright
OL,6,Fevening, with plenty of late sunny
OL,7,Fspells. It will remain dry and
OL,8,Fgenerally clear overnight, with the
OL,9,Fbrisk northeast breeze persisting.
OL,10,FBecoming rather cool in sheltered
OL,11,Finland spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA dry day with long sunny
OL,14,Fspells. Feeling warm inland but
OL,15,Ftempered by the fresh to strong
OL,16,Feasterly wind, and feeling noticeably
OL,17,Fcooler along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
