OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FLong
OL,6,Fsunny spells Thursday, but rather
OL,7,Fwindy. Winds easing Friday and
OL,8,FSaturday, with sunny intervals and an
OL,9,Fincreasing risk of showers.
OL,10,FTemperatures rising, perhaps becoming
OL,11,Fvery warm in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
